# .gitignore
# Ignores generated IBM Bob workspace settings and rule bundles that should not be tracked as source.
# This exists so ibm-bob/mode-pack remains the single source of truth for generated Bob assets.
# RELEVANT FILES: ibm-bob/mode-pack/modes/custom_modes.source.yaml, ibm-bob/mode-pack/scripts/install_mode_pack.py, ibm-bob/mode-pack/README.md
.bob/custom_modes.yaml
.bob/rules-*/
.bob/ibm-bob/
artifacts/ibm-bob/
ibm-bob/mode-pack/scripts/__pycache__/
